name: print
description: Print objects to the text stream file, separated by sep and followed by end.

name: len
description: Return the length (number of items) of an object.

name: range
description: Return an iterable sequence of numbers.

name: enumerate
description: Return an iterator yielding pairs of an index and value from the iterable.

name: open
arguments: file, mode='r', buffering=-1, encoding=None, errors=None, newline=None, closefd=True, opener=None
description: Open file and return a corresponding file object.
